#text=I was watching a cooking show yesterday on television about different recipes for cake mix cakes .
#text=I saw a recipe that looked good .
#text=I had a Red Velvet chocolate cake mix in a box and the blueberries required .
#text=I 'm too adventurous for my own good .
#text=I tossed the blueberries with sugar and put them in the baking dish .
#text=I then mixed butter and a little milk with the cake mix .
#text=I put it on top of the blueberries .
#text=It was supposed to be like a cobbler .
#text=The bottom was all watery and the cake mix was super mushy because of all the liquid .
#text=The first couple of bites were okay .
#text=That was about all anyone could eat .
#text=I even tried to get the juice out .
